Blocks.Text: nertive queue of people in the bus station,
waiting to be transported to Dinas. And
when he went to Morfydd's house, all
he found was Morydd's mam, working
herself up proper. getting dark, now.
The conductor writched on the lights.
The beleaguesed passengers peered out of
the windows. Little to be seen, only a
few lone star, and the distant earth
brooding in her shroud of mist.
